But `(image g) ∘ (image f)` is the function `fun (s : Set U) ↦ (image g (image f s))`, which is `{g(f(x)) | x ∈ s}`. By hypothesis `g ∘ f = id`, so `g(f(x)) = x`, so `image g (image f s) = s`. 

